description:
Thank you all for your amazing support! Today we've put together a compilation of 10 Animated Bible stories for you to enjoy all in one go! So sit back and enjoy some of our most popular videos, and stay tuned because we're bringing LOTS more amazing Bible stories to you soon! ❤️

Don't forget to hit the SUBSCRIBE button, giving us a thumbs up, comment your thoughts below and share this video with your friends and family! Every like, share and comment helps us bring more videos your way! ❤️

00:00 - Story of Samson
02:22 - Jonah & the Whale
05:28 - Elijah the Prophet of Fire
08:29 - Daniel in the Lions Den
11:19 - Cain and Abel
13:29 - How God Created the World
15:45 - Jesus Goes to Hell
18:04 - Jesus Tempted by Satan
20:16 - Story of John the Baptist
22:41 - Sermon on the Mount
